title: 🏆 You Did It! You're a Cashback Showdown Champion!
body:
Congratulations on making it to the top of the leaderboard! Your savvy cashback moves earned you a winning spot in the Cashback Showdown.💰

Your prize is being processed and will be credited soon. You'll be able to see it in your Earnings page once ready. Enjoy the rewards! 🔥
